uthor-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i/poem-DMtXWP8rDD7C2qq-tlbP-A">Thuật hoài - 述懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-C%C3%B4-C%E1%BA%ADp/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ho%C3%A0n-Vi%E1%BB%87t-l%C6%B0u-bi%E1%BB%87t-D%E1%BB%B1-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ch%C6%B0-c%C3%B4ng/poem-bL0oyuO88zcHPtQnM6GY6w">Tương hoàn Việt lưu biệt Dự Chương chư công - 將還越留別豫章諸公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-C%C3%B4-C%E1%BA%ADp/author-lsyoZQqnlylmCScCQiPutQ">Độc Cô Cập</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C4%A9-%C3%81i/%E1%BB%A8c-T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-xu%C3%A2n-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-U_9NDvtNtDQ93yFioKTHVg">Ức Tây Hồ xuân cảnh - 憶西湖春景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C4%A9-%C3%81i/author-WXTqpLFjop7jMgrdcNHaAg">Phạm Sĩ Ái</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-Nh%C3%A2n/Xu%C3%A2n-v%C3%A3n/poem-H9yELQlvjV5kWUIVP-1vIg">Xuân vãn - 春晚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%E1%BB%87p-Nh%C3%A2n/author-lVq0c6nfaKZdZ1zJHdkYzA">Diệp Nhân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
